&lt;li&gt;Rich product content management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-language catalog support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SEO-friendly URLs and metadata&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product recommendation engine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced search and filtering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
